Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.53,1:09:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}却又有点像军人同志
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.60,1:09:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}有点奇怪
